results.name: Number of non-isomorphic intersecting set multipartitions (multisets of sets) of weight n with empty intersection.
comment: A set multipartition is intersecting if no two parts are disjoint. The weight of a set multipartition is the sum of sizes of its parts. Weight is generally not the same as number of vertices.
